item.title: Free - All Right Now
item.description:

Oh—- there she stood
in the street–
Smiling from her head-
to her feet
I said hey–
what is this–
Now baby maybe maybe
she’s in need
Of a kiss
I said hey-
What your name– baby
maybe we can see thing
The same
now don’t you wait–
Or hesitate–
let’s move
Before they raise
the parking rent
All right now– baby
it’s all right now–
All right now– baby
it’s all right now–
I took her home-
to my place–
Watching every move
on her face–
She said look
what’s your game–
Baby
are you tryin’ to
Put me in shame
I said slow
Don’t go so fast—
don’t you think
That love- can last
she said love
Lord above–
now you tryin’ to
Trick me in love-
all right now– baby
It’s all right now–
all right now–
Baby
it’s all right now–

it’s all right now–

it’s all right now–

it’s all——
All right now——–
baby baby baby

right now- yeah-

together-
